-Hi.
-Hello, sir.

13
00:01:51,528 --> 00:01:52,654
Hi.

14
00:01:52,737 --> 00:01:54,614
-Sir.
-Sir!

15
00:01:54,697 --> 00:01:57,158
-You changed your hair!
