20
00:02:04,415 --> 00:02:06,292
-You look stunning.
-You look good.

21
00:02:06,376 --> 00:02:07,877
-Bye!
-See you later, sir!

22
00:02:15,802 --> 00:02:17,137
This is all thanks to Hee-kyung's…

