46
00:03:17,572 --> 00:03:18,698
Seo-jun!

47
00:03:19,741 --> 00:03:21,701
I was going to call you in anyway.

48
00:03:21,784 --> 00:03:22,994
Come stand next to them.

49
00:03:23,077 --> 00:03:25,872
