61
00:03:51,648 --> 00:03:53,066
I was also in the fight.

62
00:03:54,317 --> 00:03:56,069
This is absolutely outrageous.

63
00:03:56,152 --> 00:03:57,528
My goodness.

64
00:03:58,196 --> 00:03:59,239
